---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="InterIXW - Internet Technology, Software Tools & Digital Innovation"
  description="Latest news on internet technology, SaaS and cloud computing, cybersecurity trends, web development tools, digital transformation, and tech startup innovation."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">InterIXW</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">InterIXW</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Internet Technology & Digital Innovation Hub</h1>
    <p>Your trusted source for internet technology news, SaaS and cloud computing insights, cybersecurity trends, and the latest in digital transformation.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Internet Technology News</h2>
      <p>Stay ahead with breaking coverage of internet infrastructure, 5G and fiber expansion, edge computing breakthroughs, and the protocols shaping the next generation of connectivity.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>SaaS & Cloud Computing</h2>
      <p>In-depth analysis of cloud platforms, serverless architecture, multi-cloud strategies, and the SaaS tools transforming how businesses build, deploy, and scale their operations.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Cybersecurity Trends</h2>
      <p>Critical updates on zero-trust security, ransomware defense, AI-powered threat detection, vulnerability disclosures, and best practices for protecting digital assets.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Web Development Tools</h2>
      <p>Reviews and guides on the latest frameworks, IDEs, CI/CD pipelines, headless CMS platforms, and developer productivity tools powering modern web applications.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Digital Transformation</h2>
      <p>How enterprises leverage AI, automation, and data analytics to modernize workflows. Case studies on successful digital initiatives across industries worldwide.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Tech Startups & Innovation</h2>
      <p>Spotlight on emerging startups, venture funding rounds, disruptive technologies, and the entrepreneurs driving the next wave of software and internet innovation.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>
